text: Ali Zaky (born 1930) is an Egyptian gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Egypt Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
